{"tid":2500836,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本首架全球鷹無人機完成首飞","createTime":"2021-04-23T02:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T10:12:05.000Z","uid":294518,"like":3,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6ca9866fbced5f8bd0cd4f15486ea3e8cb086a59","tid":2500836,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T02:59:36.000Z","msg":"日本首架全球鷹無人機完成首飞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thedefensepost.com/2021/04/20/japan-global-hawk-drone-maiden-flight/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedefensepost.com%2F2021%2F04%2F20%2Fjapan-global-hawk-drone-maiden-flight%2F&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrYoP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=cc899f06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thedefensepost.com/2021/04/20/japan-global-hawk-drone-maiden-flight/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdCvrtj8DoE8TcjPHkYU2HtE1bb2AtQqeeHMYY1146ap3?filename=n2UyTV7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2UyTV7.png&h=17483bcb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b6883464a5af2c2d81ac351822b2f28d9ce5656","tid":2500836,"uid":395358,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:01:53.000Z","msg":"樓主rip"},{"pid":"0de2b94a191bed4c6bc0660975d2a9a56816f667","tid":2500836,"uid":294518,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:02:32.000Z","msg":"美國國防製造商諾斯羅普&middot;格魯門（Northrop Grumman）公司發表聲明，日本向其訂購的三架 RQ-4B 「全球鷹」 無人偵查機的第一架已經建造完成，上周在加利福尼亞州的帕姆代爾進行了首次試飛。這架「全球鷹」 無人偵查機首飛成功預示著日本的高空情報遙測能力即將得到大幅增強。<br />\n<br />\n諾斯洛普&middot;格魯門公司組建於 1994 年，是世界第 4 大軍工生產廠商（2010 年）、最大的雷達製造商。著名的遠程轟炸機 B-21 和 B-52 就是由該公司生產。<br />\n<br />\n2018 日本和格魯門公司簽署了這份價值 4.9 億美元的承包合同，包括對「全球鷹」無人偵查機相關設備、零部件和後勤保障提供支持。<br />\n<br />\n日本購置能夠在 60,000 英尺（18,288 米）高空飛行超過 30 小時的遙控監視飛機，將增強日本的海空監視能力。"},{"pid":"5887da2bccb6396e5743d78d84ffa42eebecd547","tid":2500836,"uid":198278,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:03:08.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"6da7b3b8af677d9b0d948729ae57951ecb93bfdc","tid":2500836,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:04:38.000Z","msg":"據《星條旗報》報道，日本政府發言人表示，這些無人機將在今年或以後部署在日本航空自衛隊的三澤空軍基地。<br />\n<br />\n全球鷹 RQ-4 具有全天候不間斷高空遙測地面實時數據和快速反應的能力，同時提供高分辨率圖像。此外，該無人機還通過其戰場機載通信節點為空中和地面用戶提供通信中繼支持。<br />\n<br />\n諾斯羅普&middot;格魯曼公司副總裁兼自主系統總經理簡&middot;畢曉普（Jane Bishop）說：「非武裝的 RQ-4B 全球鷹將為日本提供蒐集到的高空偵察信息，支持日本航空自衛隊保護邊界、監測潛在威脅和在需要時提供人道主義援助的任務。」"},{"pid":"6a94327471f72916c3e170f5f9f4afadda5ce562","tid":2500836,"uid":98223,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4b6883464a5af2c2d81ac351822b2f28d9ce5656","tid":2500836,"uid":395358,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:01:53.000Z","msg":"樓主rip"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:05:26.000Z","msg":"樓主rip"},{"pid":"72580a872ffc56d046406253a0832ab29f2bfe33","tid":2500836,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:14:18.000Z","msg":"Chinese giant Huawei was able to eavesdrop on ANY conversation on Dutch mobile network and knew which numbers were tapped by police or intelligence agencies<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-9487631/Chinese-giant-Huawei-able-eavesdrop-conversation-Dutch-mobile-network.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-9487631%2FChinese-giant-Huawei-able-eavesdrop-conversation-Dutch-mobile-network.html&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrYoP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=5e9d0e92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-9487631/Chinese-giant-Huawei-able-eavesdrop-conversation-Dutch-mobile-network.html</a><br />\n華為能監控所有荷蘭KPN的移動用戶和對話"},{"pid":"d2ba96fc41175e86bf4613bd8039b052503a2a0d","tid":2500836,"uid":59084,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:14:45.000Z","msg":"成條座頭鯨咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32049a01e366443e2a4210d17ca6870ba3179dd","tid":2500836,"uid":5134